c.name: type=mission_building,faction=coastguard,difficuty=0,probability=1,title=Boat shed is on fire,description=The Green boat shed at Beginner Coastguard Outpost is on fire. The maintenance engineer reports that the door control panel caught fire due to a short circuit. It's a small electrical fire and they are not equipped to fight it.

type=mission_building,faction=coastguard,difficuty=0,probability=1,title=Small cottage is on fire,description=Doctors from St. Sebastian Hospital have reported seeing smoke coming from the cottage at Beginner Coastguard Outpost. They can't be certain if there are casualties.

type=mission_building,faction=coastguard,difficuty=0.3,probability=0.3,title=Radio tower is on fire,description=Hospital staff responded that they see a small plume of smoke coming from the radio tower at the Beginner Coastguard Outpost.

type=mission_building,faction=coastguard,difficuty=0,probability=1,title=Radio dish is on fire,description=Dispatchers at TT Coastguard Outpost are reporting that the radio dish on the top of the ATC tower caught fire. They can't extinguish it by themselves and they are afraid it will spread. All staff have been evacuated.

type=mission_building,faction=coastguard,difficuty=0.2,probability=1,title=ATC tower is on fire,description=Emergency call from TT Coastguard Outpost. Dispatchers say that they are trapped in the ATC tower by a fire downstairs. No reports about casualties so far.

type=mission_building,faction=coastguard,difficuty=0.2,probability=1,title=ATC tower is on fire,description=Emergency call from TT Coastguard Outpost. Dispatchers says that they are trapped in ATC tower by the fire downstairs. No reports about casualties so far.

type=mission_building,faction=coastguard,difficuty=0,probability=1,title=Hangar is on fire,description=The hangar is on fire at Kutyax Coastguard Outpost. A mechanic says that fire started from a short circuit when he tried to open the doors of the hangar. There are no casualties and all staff have been evacuated from the buildings nearby.

type=mission_building,faction=coastguard,difficuty=0,probability=1,title=Hangar is on fire,description=Mechanics report that motor oil caught fire in their hangar at Kutyax Coastguard Outpost and they are afraid that fire can spread to the adjacent buildings. There are no casualties and all staff have been evacuated already.

type=mission_building,faction=transport,difficuty=0.1,probability=1,title=Building is on fire,description=Fire right next to ATC building at Kutyax Coastguard Outpost. Dispatcher reports that there is a fire from their small dumpster but no one can handle it. They are afraid that the fire can spread to their main building and there are still some staff inside.

type=mission_building,faction=coastguard,difficuty=0.3,probability=0.8,title=Wood planks are on fire,description=According to a report the harbour storage of wood planks caught fire. There are no casualties but the manager is afraid of fire spread.

type=mission_building,faction=coastguard,difficuty=0,probability=1,title=Building is on fire,description=Emergency call from the Harbour Logistics Center. The garage part of their office building is on fire. The safety officer reports that not all staff members are evacuated and there are still some workers inside. There is also a risk of further fire spread to constructions nearby.

type=mission_building,faction=coastguard,difficuty=0.2,probability=1,title=Building is on fire,description=Emergency call from the Harbour Logistics Center. Their office building is on fire. The safety officer evacuated some workers but there are still a few people inside.

type=mission_building,faction=coastguard,difficuty=0,probability=0.5,title=Building is on fire,description=Fire at docks of Three Rocks Coastguard Outpost. According to reports the fire is in a small container office. There are no casualties and no risk of further fire spread.

type=mission_building,faction=coastguard,difficuty=0,probability=0.4,title=Hangar is on fire,description=Hangar at Three Rocks Coastguard Outpost is on fire. Engineer says that they were testing the tsunami warning system and it seems that there was a short circuit. There are no casualties and no risk of further fire spread.

type=mission_building,faction=coastguard,difficuty=0.5,probability=0.3,title=Building is on fire,description=Emergency call from Three Rocks Coastguard Outpost. Dispatcher reports that they are trapped by fire and can't escape.

type=mission_building,faction=navy,difficuty=0.5,probability=0.5,title=Radio tower is on fire,description=ATC dispatcher of Military Base reports that their radio tower is on fire. There are no casualties but they have no equipment to fight the fire at that height.

type=mission_building,faction=navy,difficuty=0.3,probability=0.3,title=Military tent is on fire,description=Emergency call from Military Base. According to the report the big tent is on fire and many soldiers are still inside. They are afraid that the fire will spread to other tents nearby.

type=mission_building,faction=navy,difficuty=0.5,probability=1,title=Building is on fire,description=Emergency call from Military Base. According to the report their ATC building is on fire and many staff are still inside. They are trapped upstairs and can't fight the fire.

type=mission_building,faction=transport,difficuty=0.3,probability=1,title=Building is on fire,description=Emergency call from the Airport. According to a dispatcher report the entrance to the ATC building is on fire blocking the exit. There are some passengers inside too.

type=mission_building,faction=civilian,difficuty=0,probability=1,title=Small generator is on fire,description=Sea Fort guide reports that their diesel generator caught fire and they are afraid it will spread. All the staff members and tourists are evacuated already.

type=mission_building,faction=civilian,difficuty=0.4,probability=1,title=Sea Fort is on fire,description=Emergency call from Sea Fort. The manager reports that their guides and group of tourists are trapped by fire. There is no intel on the location of casualties. The signal inside is very low due to the thick walls of the fort so there is no way to contact them.

type=mission_building,faction=whocare,difficuty=0.3,probability=0.1,title=Tree is on fire,description=Doctors from St. Sebastian Hospital message that an old tree caught fire from a lightning strike. They afraid that the fire can spread to other trees nearby.

type=mission_building,faction=swpd,difficuty=0.1,probability=0.5,title=Storage is on fire,description=Small fire next to the police department office. Police officers report that their shed is on fire and they are afraid that the fire will spread. No casualties reported.

type=mission_building,faction=scientists,difficuty=0.1,probability=0.5,title=Building is on fire,description=Emergency call from scientists. Their large radio dish caught alight and they can't handle the fire spread. Fire already reached their main building and they say that there are still some people inside.

type=mission_building,faction=scientists,difficuty=0.2,probability=0.5,title=Observarory is on fire,description=Emergency call from scientists. Their observatory building caught fire and they can't extinguish it. Many scientists are still inside the building.

type=mission_building,faction=civilian,difficuty=0.1,probability=0.4,title=Lighthouse is on fire,description=Emergency call from a lighthouse keeper. According to their report a fire started downstairs and right now there is no way to leave the lighthouse.

type=mission_building,faction=uranwind,difficuty=0.1,probability=0.4,title=Building is on fire,description=Fire at Uran Wind Farm. According to an engineer report there was a short circuit during the maintenance. Now there is a small fire in power control house but they can't put it out. They afraid that it will spread to wind turbines and trees nearby.

type=mission_building,faction=atom,difficuty=0,probability=0.5,title=Building is on fire,description=Brinkfield power station manager reports that their container office at the docks is on fire. There is no risk of fire spread and no casualties.

type=mission_building,faction=atom,difficuty=0.7,probability=0.2,title=Substation is on fire,description=Emergency call from Brinkfield safety officer. According to their report there was a short circuit during the maintenance and now there is a serious fire with high risk of spread and could be explosive.

type=mission_building,faction=atom,difficuty=0.7,probability=0.2,title=Nuclear power station is on fire,description=Emergency call from Brinkfield safety officer. There is a fire inside the building and they can't get control over it. They started evacuation but some staff members are still in the offices. There is a very high risk of fire spread.

type=mission_building,faction=oil,difficuty=0.9,probability=0.2,title=Refinery is on fire,description=Emergency call from the oil refinery. A safety officer reports that there is a fire between two silos and they can't put it out. There is a very high risk of fire spread and explosion. They already started the evacuation.

type=mission_building,faction=oil,difficuty=0.9,probability=0.2,title=Refinery is on fire,description=Emergency call from oil refinery. According to the report an oil separator caught fire and workers can't put it out on their own. There is a very high risk of explosion. There is no information about casualties but staff evacuation has already started.

type=mission_building,faction=oil,difficuty=0.9,probability=0.2,title=Refinery is on fire,description=Emergency call from oil refinery. A manager reports that a fire started right next to their reformer facility and they are afraid that the fire will spread and cause an explosion. They evacuated many workers already but there are still a few people upstairs that are trapped by the fire.

type=mission_building,faction=oil,difficuty=0.2,probability=0.2,title=Oil rig is on fire,description=Emergency call from the oil rig. The manager reports that their office is on fire and some workers are still inside. The fire is contained and there is no risk of further spread.

type=mission_building,faction=oil,difficuty=0.2,probability=0.2,title=Oil rig is on fire,description=Emergency call from an oil rig. According to the report a couple of barrels caught fire right next to the office. No casualties have been reported so far but there a few people trapped inside.

type=mission_building,faction=oil,difficuty=0.2,probability=0.2,title=Oil rig is on fire,description=Emergency call from an oil rig. A fire safety officer reports a fire very close to their crude oil tanks. There is a high risk of fire spread and futher explosion

type=mission_building,faction=oil,difficuty=0.2,probability=0.4,title=Oil rig is on fire,description=Emergency call from an oil rig. The manager reports that there is a fire right next to the stairs and they can't leave the offices. Many people are trapped inside. There is no information about fire spread or risk of explosion.

type=mission_building,faction=oil,difficuty=0.9,probability=0.2,title=Refinery is on fire,description=Emergency call from an oil rig. According to manager report one of their transformers caught fire. Unfortunately it is right next to the oil tanks and they are afraid that fire will spread quickly. type=mission_building,faction=oil,difficuty=0.9,probability=0.2,title=Refinery is on fire,description=Emergency call from an oil rig. type=mission_building,faction=civilian,difficuty=0.1,probability=0.5,title=Lighthouse is on fire,description=Emergency call from Raptor Lighthouse. According to their report a fire started downstairs and right now there is no way to leave the lighthouse.

type=mission_building,faction=civilian,difficuty=0.1,probability=0.5,title=Lighthouse is on fire,description=Emergency call from Campbell Lighthouse. According to their report a fire started downstairs and there at least one lighthouse keeper still trapped upstairs.
